snippet.title: Savannah Brymer
snippet.description:
SAVANNAH BRYMER 

Hi! Thanks for stopping by my channel. My name is Sav and I make weekly lifestyle videos giving you my song suggestions, driving in my car with me, or sharing my crazy life stories in my weekly vlogs. Please make sure you subscribe and turn on your post notifications so you’re always notified when I post a new video!
